CLWE is a header-only library that can be used with CMake or directly.

CMake:
    find_package(CLWE CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE CLWE::clwe)

Direct usage:
    #include <clwe/clwe.hpp>
    #include <clwe/color_kem.hpp>

    int main() {
        clwe::ColorKEM kem{clwe::CLWEParameters(128)};
        // ... use the library
    }